c: 47
v: 20
t: Ureueng meuiman geukheun dum teuma Pakon roe hana Neubri peurintah Pakon roe hana Neupeutron surat ‘Oh ban tron surat nyan pih ka susah Surat nyang teugas geuyue jak meuprang Takalon yoh nyan na nyang geulisah Nyang na peunyaket dalam atejih Sang-sang taeu jih pingsan ka reubah Jikalon gata sang jih ka pingsan Mate beu rijang meunan sang ulah Nyang got that di jih roe watee nyan